    <string name="home_dialog_1">Good morning, students! We are Xanti and Maialen, the giants of Errenteria’s festivals.</string>
    <string name="home_dialog_2">But today we won’t go to the festivities; we’ll take a trip around Errenteria.</string>
    <string name="home_dialog_3">Along the way we’ll do some activities to make it more fun!</string>
    <string name="home_dialog_4">We will explore places and topics that are part of Errenteria’s history.</string>
    <string name="home_dialog_5">On this map you can see which places we will visit.</string>
    <string name="home_dialog_6">If you want to see everything, follow your teacher!</string>

    <string name="home_idle_1">We’re ready! Tap the button to start playing.</string>
    <string name="home_idle_2">We’re waiting for you, tap the button and let’s begin!</string>

