    <string name="azalpen_bertso_title">Didactic text</string>
    <string name="azalpen_bertso_body">Although bertsos are oral, thanks to bertso-papers (pamphlets that collected the bertsos) they could be spread throughout Euskal Herria. Thanks to those bertso-papers, today you can read and complete the bertsos of these two bertsolaris. To complete these bertsos, pay attention to the rhymes and the story they are telling.</string>

    <string name="azalpen_papresa_title">Papresa: Papermaking in Errenteria</string>
    <string name="azalpen_papresa_body">The game has two parts:\n\n❶ **PUZZLE**: You will learn the history of the Papresa factory. Complete the puzzle and read the factory’s history.\n\n❷ **RECYCLING**: Once you finish the puzzle, you must place objects in the correct container.</string>

